	<Title>
		Melatonin side effects: What are the risks?
	</Title>
	<Abstract>
		Melatonin side effects include daytime sleepiness, dizziness and headaches. Medication interactions also are possible.
	</Abstract>
	<Question>
		Is melatonin a helpful sleep aid &amp;mdash; and what should I know about melatonin side effects?
